{"tid":1553100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日遊行已上國際新聞，多謝前線手足幫手爭取時間！","createTime":"2019-09-08T13:28:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T07:47:56.000Z","uid":209873,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"25d29a48e6a01716818282ac90c66ca3a2cce772","tid":1553100,"uid":209873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:28:41.000Z","msg":"睇到全球頭版新聞已經係今日香港遊行，所以我哋今日已經成功，前線手足就算拆L咗黨鐵都唔會有任何影響，更何況香港嘅示威活動同外國嘅比根本小兒科到不得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本來好地地既和平遊行，係班仆街狗自己撩交打，要我哋提早散水又封鐵唔畀我哋走，根本錯不在我哋 <br />\n非常多謝勇敢嘅前線手足幫我地爭取時間離開，我都係求其上咗架巴士，兜咗一大圈先返到屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係唔緊要，做人要有骨氣，可不搭黨鐵就不搭！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V01wa1M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV01wa1M.jpg&h=606c8824&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"534474f30ac7114cbacfaca61dadcea66c32730b","tid":1553100,"uid":22558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:31:41.000Z","msg":"係人都知狗潑火 佢地扮示威者搞事全世界都知架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 班3毛成鳩日話呢樣果樣 好撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 阻鳩住我睇post"},{"pid":"6744db5be555907e60c9d26c4f84619d5e7ae4b0","tid":1553100,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T14:03:28.000Z","msg":"狗亂咬人，勇武法師護巿民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1b725f21279332079abcec6a60543963f176b86","tid":1553100,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:47:56.000Z","msg":"<